snippet.title: OFFICIAL #OMG​ RELEASE TRAILER - Muffin Fight #VR #Arena
snippet.description:
Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1506940/Muffin_Fight/

What is it?  Well, you've always needed this and just never realized it!  Imagine cooking, muffins, fighting, friends... Blueberries... Bananas...  And OH yes... chocolate!

Launches February 19 on Steam.  The day before International Muffin Day!

Let's get dangerous!
* Warning may contain traces of nuts
